## 

<span key="fa77b3543fce41098925181795772ebf"><span offset-key="fa77b3543fce41098925181795772ebf:0">Glossary</span></span>

### 

<span key="35848bbbeaf44c7299c88cf9772c7817"><span offset-key="35848bbbeaf44c7299c88cf9772c7817:0">Product</span></span>

<span key="5cd85a1d34df4291aa448c93c856ddb2"><span offset-key="5cd85a1d34df4291aa448c93c856ddb2:0">A business term for a set of applications, service or other resources that provide some value to an end-user or other system.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="61905cebdf92488a874622de57d6509c"><span offset-key="61905cebdf92488a874622de57d6509c:0">A Product may exist for a very long time or sometimes not long at all</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="78a8efc4d5be42fda945dc311760ca46"><span offset-key="78a8efc4d5be42fda945dc311760ca46:0">A Product may be implemented in many different ways and the implementation may change completely at some point during its lifespan</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="50eb2d932b6345f180f5ecfcc635865d"><span offset-key="50eb2d932b6345f180f5ecfcc635865d:0">A </span>*Product*<span offset-key="50eb2d932b6345f180f5ecfcc635865d:2"> is a logical construct (aka logical entity), meaning it's just a name that groups together a set of People, Projects and Resources</span></span>

### 

<span key="00de1b553eac49c797ed0abbf4c9a93b"><span offset-key="00de1b553eac49c797ed0abbf4c9a93b:0">Product Role</span></span>

<span key="62c712039a8345199c79d9b34955d708"><span offset-key="62c712039a8345199c79d9b34955d708:0">A set of skills and responsibilities required to make a </span>*Product*<span offset-key="62c712039a8345199c79d9b34955d708:2"> successful. </span>*Product Roles*<span offset-key="62c712039a8345199c79d9b34955d708:4"> are filled by people who have the required skills (or will learn them quickly!) and will take on the responsibilities to make the </span>*Product*<span offset-key="62c712039a8345199c79d9b34955d708:6"> successful.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="df3c03bc017b4a4dbc4fb02043c8f907"><span offset-key="df3c03bc017b4a4dbc4fb02043c8f907:0">Typical </span>*Product Roles*<span offset-key="df3c03bc017b4a4dbc4fb02043c8f907:2">:</span></span>

    -   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

        <span key="f70ba0d485f4492b9efcb93cef9583e0"><span offset-key="f70ba0d485f4492b9efcb93cef9583e0:0">Product Manager, Product Stakeholder, Product Designer, etc.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="c99bbc9e955c422580f8278cdd026a0f">*Product Roles*<span offset-key="c99bbc9e955c422580f8278cdd026a0f:1"> can change over time, as the needs and the lifecycle of the Product evolves</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="e5d456fda0cf4949ba3c8a071cf2163e"><span offset-key="e5d456fda0cf4949ba3c8a071cf2163e:0">A </span>*Product Role*<span offset-key="e5d456fda0cf4949ba3c8a071cf2163e:2"> is a logical construct; it's just a name given to a set of skills and responsibilities.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="8772df32dbc347348c29906cf0186aa3"><span offset-key="8772df32dbc347348c29906cf0186aa3:0">When you are part of a </span>*Product*<span offset-key="8772df32dbc347348c29906cf0186aa3:2">, you are actually playing a </span>*Role*<span offset-key="8772df32dbc347348c29906cf0186aa3:4"> on that </span>*Product*<span offset-key="8772df32dbc347348c29906cf0186aa3:6">. Your </span>*Product Role*<span offset-key="8772df32dbc347348c29906cf0186aa3:8"> defines the items you a responsible or accountable for.</span></span>

### 

<span key="cc60f484e3c34fcd9804390c61e04a30"><span offset-key="cc60f484e3c34fcd9804390c61e04a30:0">Project</span></span>

<span key="cefd636733e047b89c79ac48c41bab15"><span offset-key="cefd636733e047b89c79ac48c41bab15:0">A business term for a group people that are working to build, fix, extend or otherwise enhance a </span>*Product*<span offset-key="cefd636733e047b89c79ac48c41bab15:2"> for some period of time.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="aec58210da83468e983db1db0eedacc8"><span offset-key="aec58210da83468e983db1db0eedacc8:0">A </span>*Project*<span offset-key="aec58210da83468e983db1db0eedacc8:2"> is associated with one and only one </span>*Product*<span offset-key="aec58210da83468e983db1db0eedacc8:4">.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="cd280e8fd9374f9092cb56b14b1c0443"><span offset-key="cd280e8fd9374f9092cb56b14b1c0443:0">A </span>*Project*<span offset-key="cd280e8fd9374f9092cb56b14b1c0443:2"> has a pre-defined set of </span>*Roles*<span offset-key="cd280e8fd9374f9092cb56b14b1c0443:4"> required for the </span>*Project*<span offset-key="cd280e8fd9374f9092cb56b14b1c0443:6"> to be successful.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="ebea701782fd446f8518ad1c8e81b403"><span offset-key="ebea701782fd446f8518ad1c8e81b403:0">People are assigned to one or more </span>*Roles*<span offset-key="ebea701782fd446f8518ad1c8e81b403:2"> on a </span>*Project*<span offset-key="ebea701782fd446f8518ad1c8e81b403:4">, which helps guides their work.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="2123800c50f34c49aecd1598818306e3"><span offset-key="2123800c50f34c49aecd1598818306e3:0">A </span>*Project*<span offset-key="2123800c50f34c49aecd1598818306e3:2"> has a specific starting point and a specific end point. The end point can either be when a specific amount of time has passed or specific set of tasks have been completed.</span></span>

### 

<span key="28b6330dfc9d40d6b4e1f46b084d1c1e"><span offset-key="28b6330dfc9d40d6b4e1f46b084d1c1e:0">Project Role</span></span>

<span key="0e23ef64d38743ce8dd50444b3ccd3c3"><span offset-key="0e23ef64d38743ce8dd50444b3ccd3c3:0">A set of skills and responsibilities required to make a </span>*Project*<span offset-key="0e23ef64d38743ce8dd50444b3ccd3c3:2"> successful. </span>*Project Roles*<span offset-key="0e23ef64d38743ce8dd50444b3ccd3c3:4"> are filled by people who have the required skills (or will learn them quickly!) and will take on the responsibilities to make the </span>*Project*<span offset-key="0e23ef64d38743ce8dd50444b3ccd3c3:6"> successful.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="90d50e80398641ffa4130ba849364466"><span offset-key="90d50e80398641ffa4130ba849364466:0">Typical </span>*Project Roles*<span offset-key="90d50e80398641ffa4130ba849364466:2">:</span></span>

    -   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

        <span key="24d3a47413dc4d04a9f7833f6a5bf7fd"><span offset-key="24d3a47413dc4d04a9f7833f6a5bf7fd:0">Project Manager, Lead Engineer, UX Designer, Web Developer, Data Scientist, Mobile Engineer, etc.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="5d0d9c47def44ea49794c0b3a91e04c6">*Project Roles*<span offset-key="5d0d9c47def44ea49794c0b3a91e04c6:1"> can change over time, as the needs and the lifecycle of the </span>*Project*<span offset-key="5d0d9c47def44ea49794c0b3a91e04c6:3"> evolves</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="a691c3e934c24a3982c6a82c6d38db50"><span offset-key="a691c3e934c24a3982c6a82c6d38db50:0">A </span>*Project Role*<span offset-key="a691c3e934c24a3982c6a82c6d38db50:2"> is a logical construct; it's just a name given to a set of skills and responsibilities.</span></span>

-   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="b6a3304641f74908825c777fcb13f4b2"><span offset-key="b6a3304641f74908825c777fcb13f4b2:0">When you are part of a </span>*Project*<span offset-key="b6a3304641f74908825c777fcb13f4b2:2">, you are actually playing a </span>*Role*<span offset-key="b6a3304641f74908825c777fcb13f4b2:4"> on that </span>*Project*<span offset-key="b6a3304641f74908825c777fcb13f4b2:6">. Your </span>*Project Role*<span offset-key="b6a3304641f74908825c777fcb13f4b2:8"> defines the items you a responsible or accountable for.</span></span>

### 

<span key="5426227fed344227b4411aa7987869a8"><span offset-key="5426227fed344227b4411aa7987869a8:0">AWS Product Account</span></span>

<span key="be75ded61d4440cabff06479e9f6420d"><span offset-key="be75ded61d4440cabff06479e9f6420d:0">An AWS account that hosts all of the various AWS resources required to run a particular student </span>*Product*<span offset-key="be75ded61d4440cabff06479e9f6420d:2">.</span></span>

![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)

<span key="76c623ed0c57488db708e6d825035423"><span offset-key="76c623ed0c57488db708e6d825035423:0">There is only one AWS account per </span>*Product*<span offset-key="76c623ed0c57488db708e6d825035423:2"> that is shared by all </span>*Project*<span offset-key="76c623ed0c57488db708e6d825035423:4"> teams.</span></span>
